                             'E_vaz_ive' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'E_vaz_ive' is a @{"Workbench game" link play} where you have to move a coloured
hexagonal shape from the top of the game board to the exit tile,
located somewhere at the bottom of the board. To move, you must
follow the coloured links in order to go from one tile to another.
Also, to complete a game board, none of the small hexagonal shapes
that are located on the game tiles, including the one on the exit
tile, must be either in black or white.

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

